data.description: Simply amazing, completely updated 4-bedroom 2-bathroom waterfront pool home located on over 15,000+ sqft lot located Coral Springs Country Club/ no HOA. When someone say turnkey home, this is what they are talking about.   You have to come take a tour to fully understand how beautiful this home is. Owner has updated and upgraded this entire home. New roof installed in 2022, impact windows and doors, travertine pool deck with pebble rock pool and complete outdoor kitchen. 24*48 tile continuous, plantation shutters, custom closets, updated bathrooms and kitchen. new pool pump/salt filtration, water filtration system just to list a few of the updates and upgrades.You don't want to miss out on this one.MORE PICTURES COMMING SOON
